parameters: ガブ
We became husband and wife and started a new life together.
Even so, it was a peaceful everyday life, not much different from before.

We would hunt, Umi would cook the game, and the three of us, including
Mi-A, would eat together...

We'd share any excess food with our neighbors, and in return, we'd
sometimes receive fruit...

Occasionally, we'd have petty arguments, but usually, Mi-A would meow to
mediate, I'd apologize first, followed by Umi, and we'd make up.

Through repeating 'thank you' and 'I'm sorry' in our daily lives, we grew
accustomed to our relationship as a married couple.

I imagined that eventually, our two children would be born and join us in
this circle of 'thank you' and 'I'm sorry,' living life with laughter and
anger.
Time passed in such a way, and a year went by...

Umi: "Kru. The chief has been urging me to take over as the next chief
soon."

Kru: "Hmm, that's true. Quite some time has passed since then... I guess I
need to go and listen to what he has to say."
Umi: "Yes. Go ahead. I'll be waiting with dinner ready."
Kru: "Right... I'm off then!"
"Talk to the chieftain."
Kru "Huh... Umi?"

Kru "Did she go to the bathroom or something... I hope... she comes back
soon..."
Kru "Good morning, Umi... yawn... It's early, isn't it..."
物憂げ1
Umi "Yeah! Good morning, Kru!"

Kru "Oh, you're unusually energetic this morning... Normally you're sleepy
and grumpy..."

Umi "Is that so...? I just happened to wake up feeling refreshed today!
Maybe that's why I'm feeling energetic?"
Kru "I see... It would be nice if you could feel like this every day."
Umi "Every day..."
Kru "Umi?"
Umi "Huh? Ah... yeah, it would be nice to be this energetic every day..."
Umi "It would be nice..."
Kru "Hey? Umi, you've got some lint on you?"
物憂げ2
Umi "Don't come any closer!"
Kru "!!!! What's wrong, Umi?"
物憂げ3

Umi "Ah... haha... Oh! It's sweat from sleeping! I sweated a lot... I
wonder if it smells."

Kru "You don't have to worry about that... I've never thought Umi smelled
bad."
Umi "Thank you... Umi... I'm going to take a bath..."
Kru "Umi... What's gotten into her?"
At that time, I didn't understand anything.
The reason behind Umi's smile, why she said not to come closer...
The cats meowed... Their cries echoed with the dryness of Umi's absence...
アイキャッチ4
アイキャッチ4タイトル
Kru: "So, that's why I have to go and take on the three trials."
Umi: "I see..."

Kru: "And then, the chief asked me to take Banka along. So the two of us
will go together."
Umi: "Umi will go too..."
Kru: "Eh? No, it's dangerous, so Umi should stay and watch the house."
Umi: "No... Umi will go too. It's worrying with just the two of you..."
Kru: "Eh... But..."

Umi: "If it's just the two of you, you'll only get hurt. It'll be safer
with Umi there."
Kru: "...That's true. Well then, it's an adventure after a long time."
Umi: "Yeah... an adventure."
Mi-A: "Meow~"
"Overcome the first trial"
Umi "Is Banka coming again..."
Kru "Yeah, he helped us out last time, right?"

Banka "Miss Umi! If you're feeling unwell again, please leave it to me."
Kru "?... Shall we go then?"
"Break through the second trial."
